{
  "stem": "23090.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let me say this to you, Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kelman, that-- that the war-- you know, the war just didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew about it, or the elders knew about it, so-- so the conversation was way, way before the actual invasion, because Hitler was already acting up very much in the-- in the entire European area so that when the elders did discuss it-- and that's pre-war or pre-invasion-- we were already scared at that point, as a child, as an adult, or whatever capacity.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we say pre-war or during war, to me, I was-- I was being scared already prior to the invasion.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the gatherings were basically 90%, if not more, what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How are we going to cope with it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There-- I heard that this one is already there and this is-- invasion is there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have-- I had a couple uncles in the army who-- who-- my uncles and my dad was worried that he was already killed in the-- during the battles.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we already had plenty of preparation for the actual-- until the actual invasion really happened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So as a child, I already formed my call it scared mode.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was already in that scared mode, and that's how we lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the interim, as a child, you forget that for the time being and you play with other children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But when you get home, that dismal, that sad, and that worry was on everyone's face.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it was very difficult to escape it pre-war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Did you go to school?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to the first-- the first grade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was seven years old when the-- perhaps the second grade-- I went to what we called a cheder.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
